article.title: Jaynes Assigned Dual-Hatted Role at Pax River
article.author: Beverly Schaeffer
article.text: Rear Adm. Cindy L. Jaynes, USN, has been nominated for assignment as commander, Fleet Readiness Centers, Patuxent River, Maryland, and assistant commander for logistics and industrial operations (AIR-6.0) Naval Air Systems Command, Patuxent River.
